  "name": "Sarutobi Clan",
  "type": "feat",
  "system": {
    "subType": "trait",
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The Sarutobi clan is one of the most renowned clans in the ninja world. They have produced many strong shinobi, most notably the Third Hokage of Konoha gakure, Hiruzen Sarutobi. They do not possess a specific bloodline like some clans, and yet they are still a group that could compare with the strongest of ninja clans.</p><p><b>Source:</b> Mechanics/Character_Options/Occupations/Community Compendium/Sarutobi Clan.md</p><p><b>Category:</b> Community Compendium</p><p><b>Prerequisite:</b> Age 8+</p><p><b>Class Skills:</b> Select 3 from Balance, Concentration, Escape Artist, Hide, Knowledge (Ninja Lore), Listen, Ninjutsu, Sleight of Hand, Taijutsu.</p><p><b>Feat:</b> Select one from Acrobatic, Advanced Study, Archaic Weapons Proficiency, Athletic, Combat Martial Arts, Defensive Martial Arts, Dodge, Genin, Genius Ninja, Nin Weapon Proficiency, Ninjutsu Adept, Taijutsu Adept.</p><p><b>Wealth Bonus Increase:</b> +1</p><p><b>Reputation Bonus Increase:</b> +2</p><p><b>Affiliation:</b> You require 1 less success to learn Konoha specific techniques.</p>"
    },
